  <div class="container" id="join">
    <div class="section">
    <div class="col s12 center">
          <h3><i class="mdi-content-send brown-text"></i></h3>
          <h4>Procedure to Join IITK Climbing</h4>
          <p class="left-align light">If you want to try out once, you can get a day pass. If you are interested, you can get a permanent slot.</p>
          
      <!--   Icon Section   -->
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col s12 m4">
          <div class="icon-block">
            <h2 class="center brown-text"><i class="material-icons">flash_on</i></h2>
            <h5 class="center">Permanent slot</h5>

            <p class="light">
You can email our coach, Pushpendra Singh (climbingearth@gmail.com) about the availability of a slot. If there is an opening, he will assign a temporary slot and send an email with a deadline. You need to pay before the deadline (payment procedure given below) and send the receipt and filled out waiver form to him. Please donâ€™t pay before getting a temporary slot email from the coach, it will not be counted. Please note that if you are absent in your slot for multiple days without notification, your slot will be given to the next person. 
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="col s12 m4">
          <div class="icon-block">
            <h2 class="center brown-text"><i class="material-icons">flash_on</i></h2>
            <h5 class="center">Timings for climbing sessions</h5>

            <p class="light">Timings for climbing sessions: We have sessions every evening and most mornings. The evening sessions run from 6pm onwards. Morning sessions depend on the time of the year and can range from 5:30-7:30 in summers to 7:00-8:30 in winters.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
		  <div class="row">
        <div class="col s12 m4">
          <div class="icon-block">
            <h2 class="center brown-text"><i class="material-icons">group</i></h2>
            <h5 class="center">Day pass</h5>

            <p class="light">
		You can visit us at the wall when there is a climbing session going on. If there is a room, the instructor will ask you to pay for the day pass. Pay the day fee (payment procedure given below) and try climbing once.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="col s12 m4">
          <div class="icon-block">
            <h2 class="center brown-text"><i class="material-icons">settings</i></h2>
            <h5 class="center">Special events</h5>

            <p class="light">
You can also participate in one of the regularly organized climbing workshops (though they are sold out pretty quickly), generally the email is sent once in two months.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
		</div>

      </div>


      <h5>Fees Details and Payment Procedure</h5>
            <table class="responsive-table centered">
        <thead>
          <tr>
              <th>Members</th>
              <th>Daily</th>
              <th>Monthly</th>
              <th>Semester (4 months)</th>
              <th>Annual (12 months)</th>
          </tr>
        </thead>

        <tbody>
          <tr>
            <td>Student</td>
            <td>50</td>
            <td>100</td>
            <td>300</td>
            <td>600</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>Staff/RA</td>
            <td>50</td>
            <td>150</td>
            <td>450</td>
            <td>900</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>Faculty/Dependent</td>
            <td>50</td>
            <td>200</td>
            <td>600</td>
            <td>1200</td>
          </tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>
           
	</div>
     <p>* Even if you pay in the middle of the month, you will be charged for the entire month. For example, if you pay for one month on 23rd August 2022, it will be valid till 31st August 2022. </p>
     <p style="align-items: left;">To pay the fee follow the steps below: 
     <ol>
<li>Login to <a href="https://www.onlinesbi.sbi/sbicollect/icollecthome.htm">SBI-I Collect.</a></li>
<li>After selecting Uttar Pradesh then Educational Institutions and then Indian Institute of Technology Kanpur,
Select PHYSICAL EDUCATION SECTION RECEIPT.</li>
<li>Then Select NEW SPORTS COMPLEX in PAID FACILITIES and select WALL CLIMBING in SERVICES. Fill out the other required details.</li>
<li>Fill the membership fee according to the table above and pay the required amount.</li>
<li>Send the receipt and filled out <a href="Climbing_Wall_Declaration.pdf">waiver form</a> to Pushpendra Singh (climbingearth@gmail.com).</li>
<li><b> Don't pay in any other section. It will not be counted.</b> </li>
</ol>
     </p>

    </div>
