  <div class="container" id="howto">
    <div class="section">
    <div class="col s12 center">
          <h3><i class="mdi-content-send brown-text"></i></h3>
          <h4>How to climb at IITK</h4>
          
      <!--   Icon Section   -->
        <div class="row">
        <div class="col s12 m8 ">
          <div class="icon-block">
            <h2 class="center brown-text"><i class="material-icons">group</i></h2>
            <h5 class="center">Experience Focused</h5>

            <p class="light">Once you start climbing, we will record you progress. To start with, you are in the beginner category. We will teach you knots, belaying, safety protocols and techniques for climbing; the first stage is to become a belayer when you can climb and belay independently.
After some more practice, you will also learn lead climbing and can become an advanced climber. We also organize sessions where you can learn rappelling, ascending the rope, anchor building etc. to improve your skills. We keep changing the wall and it always has fresh challenges for you. 
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

    
        <div class="col s12 m4">
          <div class="icon-block">
            <h2 class="center brown-text"><i class="material-icons">settings</i></h2>
            <h5 class="center">Some Benefits</h5>

            <p class="light">
				The climb gives a sense of accomplishment and Zen. Climbing gives physical as well as mental challenges.You can build trust and create a community.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
      </div>
	</div>
    </div>
  </div> 








