  <div class="container" id="group">
    <div class="section">
    <div class="col s12 center">
          <h3><i class="mdi-content-send brown-text"></i></h3>
          <h4>Climbing group@IITK</h4>
               <p class="left-align light">
One of the perks of climbing (not just at IITK but the whole world) is that you meet people with similar interests and make friendships for life. We have a climbing group at IIT Kanpur here too.
<br/>
We climb regularly, make routes on the wall and encourage (and tease) each other to climb better. We make plans and sometimes actually go for climbing trips. These climbing trips are focussed mostly on food, in between there is a bit of climbing.
</p>
               
      <!--   Icon Section   -->
